leslie's single?

14:27.567 --> 14:29.901
The hair, the face...
All of it.

14:33.339 --> 14:36.574
All right, let's check in
and see how you guys did
with your lima bean plants.

14:36.576 --> 14:38.910
- Wayne, where's yours?
- I killed it.

14:38.912 --> 14:41.112
Why would you do that?

14:41.114 --> 14:42.981
Well, it was taking
too long.

14:42.983 --> 14:44.549
