15:55.220 --> 15:56.955
You know,
ernesto...

15:56.957 --> 15:58.957
Yes.

16:00.426 --> 16:02.961
Well, if you want it,
don't wait too long.

16:02.963 --> 16:05.563
Somebody else
is gonna bone it

16:05.565 --> 16:07.665
And own it.

16:07.667 --> 16:11.302
Actually, I'm more worried
that someone's gonna rent it
and dent it.

16:11.304 --> 16:14.572
But I gotta do something.
I just don't wanna hurt
my career.

16:14.574 --> 16:17.608
Charlie,
love is more important
than any career.

16:17.610 --> 16:21.245
And I say that
as a successful manager
of boy bands.

16:23.148 --> 16:26.284
Now, in all my years
of home invasion, no one
ever said to me,

16:26.286 --> 16:29.354
"please, don't
shoot me, mister.
I got work tomorrow."

16:29.356 --> 16:31.622
It's always,
"I got a wife and kids."

16:31.624 --> 16:34.192
Makes you reassess
what's important in life.

16:35.728 --> 16:37.662
Words of wisdom, wayne.

16:37.664 --> 16:41.733
Terrifying, disturbing,
unmedicated words of wisdom.

16:48.007 --> 16:50.341
- Hey, tom, leslie.
- Hey.

16:50.343 --> 16:51.743
You guys ready
to karaoke?

16:51.745 --> 16:54.245
By the way,
"the girl is mine,"
is mine.

16:54.247 --> 16:57.382
Dr. Rita
freudenberger, md,

16:57.384 --> 17:00.218
- Phd.
- Oh, for the love of god.

17:00.220 --> 17:03.087
I was hope's
feminist therapist.

17:03.089 --> 17:06.024
My practice combines
traditional talk therapy

17:06.026 --> 17:09.227
With a radical methodological
approach to psychology

17:09.229 --> 17:12.764
That questions
patriarchal assumptions.

17:12.766 --> 17:14.732
I want her so much.

17:14.734 --> 17:16.701
I have a proposal.

17:16.703 --> 17:19.570
As psychologists,
we're all familiar
with platt's concept

17:19.572 --> 17:21.806
Of the social trap
where individuals
acting selfishly

17:21.808 --> 17:24.742
Harm the group as a whole,
so I suggest we suspend
our campaigns

17:24.744 --> 17:27.345
Just for tonight
and celebrate hope's
birthday with dignity.

17:27.347 --> 17:29.814
- Fine.
- Fine.

17:29.816 --> 17:32.183
I'm too drunk
to get it up anyway.

17:32.185 --> 17:34.185
That's the kind of dignity
I'm looking for.

17:34.187 --> 17:36.487
First round's on me.

17:36.489 --> 17:39.624
Can we get a pitcher
of margaritas, please?

17:39.626 --> 17:42.193
Did you get the flowers
and the plane tickets to maui?

17:42.195 --> 17:44.662
I gotta say,
I'm impressed,
charlie.

17:44.664 --> 17:46.597
This is a pretty
bold move.

17:46.599 --> 17:48.599
Throwing a hail mary
here, brett.

17:48.601 --> 17:50.635
I'm breaking all the rules,
but if I don't seal
the deal tonight,

17:50.637 --> 17:53.538
She could wind up
with one of these bozos.

17:53.540 --> 17:55.473
You know, I think
this is the most
romantic thing

17:55.475 --> 17:57.375
That's ever happened
in this bar.

17:57.377 --> 18:00.778
Except for things
that have happened
on this bar.

18:00.780 --> 18:02.313
I wouldn't tell
the health inspector.

18:02.315 --> 18:04.315
It was with
the health inspector.

18:04.317 --> 18:06.651
How do you think
we got a "b"?

18:06.653 --> 18:08.719
Thanks.

18:11.290 --> 18:13.191
Here we go,
everybody.

18:15.260 --> 18:17.695
- Hi, everybody.
- Hey, the birthday
girl's here.

18:17.697 --> 18:19.831
- I'd like to propose a toast.
- I'm sorry, charlie,

18:19.833 --> 18:21.833
But something
really important
just happened

18:21.835 --> 18:24.335
- That I have to tell
you all about.
- Okay, okay.

18:24.337 --> 18:25.837
Just remember,
after you tell us,

18:25.839 --> 18:28.539
It's birthday toast
and the spanking machine.

18:29.641 --> 18:33.678
Charlie,
I've been seeing
a hypnotherapist.

18:33.680 --> 18:36.814
- Another therapist?
- Yes.

18:36.816 --> 18:38.783
And right before
I came here,

18:38.785 --> 18:43.221
He helped me recover
a traumatic memory.

18:43.223 --> 18:45.356
I discovered that

18:45.358 --> 18:48.559
My former hypnotherapist
groped me while I was under.

18:48.561 --> 18:50.661
Now, I know it is going
to take years

18:50.663 --> 18:52.730
For me to
work through this,

18:52.732 --> 18:56.801
But I'm so glad
that tonight

18:56.803 --> 18:59.504
I am with
the four people

18:59.506 --> 19:01.672
Who make me feel
truly safe

19:01.674 --> 19:03.841
<i>And who I know</i>

19:03.843 --> 19:06.844
Would never
take advantage of me.

19:08.514 --> 19:10.314
I'm sorry.
I need a moment.

19:14.786 --> 19:16.854
( laughs )
yikes.

19:19.658 --> 19:21.893
I guess we better cancel
the spanking machine.

19:23.762 --> 19:25.830
I'm out of here.

19:29.468 --> 19:31.302
Look, I don't wanna seem
insensitive here,

19:31.304 --> 19:34.672
But was that a "I'm never
gonna have sex again grope"

19:34.674 --> 19:37.642
Or "I'm not gonna have sex
for six months grope"?

19:37.644 --> 19:40.611
Are you kidding me?
What is wrong with you people?

19:40.613 --> 19:42.647
I'm just saying
as a phobia therapist,

19:42.649 --> 19:44.749
I think I still have
a shot with her.

19:44.751 --> 19:46.817
I did get her
to hold a snake.

19:48.320 --> 19:51.322
You're a disgrace.
You're all disgraces.

19:51.324 --> 19:54.358
- We need to figure out
a way to help this woman.
- You're right.

19:54.360 --> 19:57.228
I think she needs
another woman to go
talk to her.

19:57.230 --> 19:59.797
Don't let the door
hit you in the penises
on the way out.

19:59.799 --> 20:01.732
No, no, no, no, no.

20:01.734 --> 20:04.569
We're gonna stay here,
we're gonna make her
feel safe,

20:04.571 --> 20:06.771
And we're gonna try
and salvage what's left
of her birthday.

20:06.773 --> 20:08.272
And you know how?

20:08.274 --> 20:10.675
We're all gonna pitch
in to buy her some flowers

20:10.677 --> 20:13.411
And send her on
a nice vacation
to maui.

20:13.413 --> 20:15.646
I'll put it on my card
if you guys just give me
the cash.

20:17.482 --> 20:20.818
- Oh, my god.
That poor girl.
- I know. It's horrible.

20:20.820 --> 20:22.687
Well, at least she got
a free trip to maui

20:22.689 --> 20:25.389
That no one else
pitched in on.

20:25.391 --> 20:27.992
I still don't
understand why you took
this whole thing so far.

20:27.994 --> 20:30.795
I was frustrated.
I thought I found
someone who knew me.

20:30.797 --> 20:32.363
That I could
have a future with.

20:32.365 --> 20:33.831
You don't find
that every day.

20:33.833 --> 20:36.767
Oh, so it was about me.

20:36.769 --> 20:39.237
No, it wasn't.

20:39.239 --> 20:42.306
Okay. Come here
and I'll give you
a therapeutic hug.

20:42.308 --> 20:45.643
I don't want one of your
cold, machine-like hugs.

20:45.645 --> 20:48.012
I want somebody
who knows me,
who likes me,

20:48.014 --> 20:49.780
Who's ready
to make a commitment.

20:49.782 --> 20:53.351
Well, charlie.
I know you and I like you.

20:53.353 --> 20:55.419
And?

20:55.421 --> 20:57.455
And I'm willing
to be your friend

20:57.457 --> 21:00.891
And have sex
with you until you find
this mystery woman.

21:00.893 --> 21:04.328
Thanks.

21:04.330 --> 21:06.897
However long it takes.
Okay, time's up. Leave.

21:06.899 --> 21:08.899
Wait a minute,
you just said however
long it takes.

21:08.901 --> 21:11.569
- It could take forever.
- We're done for today.

21:11.571 --> 21:14.038
I have another client.
Look in the lobby, maybe
